  "signal_description": "For the table 'defaultview-217', this query summarizes the number of cases created in each month when the issue was created. It first selects the first end time of the event 'Create Issue' and truncates it to the month level. Then, it counts the number of case IDs where the event name matches 'Create Issue' and the subsequent event is 'Change Status to To Do'. The results are grouped by the month when the issue was created and ordered by the same."
